d the differences between many contrasting </div><div class="t m415 x3d h15 y602 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">entities: </div><div class="t ma8 x4d h15 y2ef ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m225 x1e h15 y2ef ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The world and the church </div><div class="t maa x4d h15 y2f0 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m19a x1e h15 y2f1 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The old person and the new </div><div class="t mac x4d h15 y2f2 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m183 x1e h15 y7cf ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selfishness and love </div><div class="t maf x4d h15 y7d0 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mc7 x1e h15 y7d0 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dissension and unity </div><div class="t mb1 x4d h15 y2f4 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m116 x1e h15 y7d1 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sin and holiness </div><div class="t mb4 x4d h15 y7d2 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m4ce x1e h15 y7d2 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Darkness and light </div><div class="t mb7 x4d h15 y608 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m5e8 x1e h15 y608 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The devil&apos;s work and God&apos;s </div><div class="t m5e9 x4d h15 y9a ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this week&apos;s lesson, we will study yet another two contrasting </div><div class="t m293 x3d h15 y7d3 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">entities—a secular family and a Christian home. In fact, marriage is </div><div class="t m162 x3d h15 y7d4 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one of the two institutions that remain from Eden. </div><div class="t m4a9 x3d h15 y7d5 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">80 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
